:INFO
The Amazon Operating Manual I Did Not Expect to Use
Working Backwards is written by two former Amazon executives who describe the \
internal culture as clearly as any management book has managed to. The press \
release backwards method sounded gimmicky to me until I actually tried it on a \
project I had been struggling to frame. Writing the imaginary customer review first \
completely changed what I thought the product was supposed to be.

:NOW
Using the working backwards method on my current project brief

:QUOTE [subtitle:Colin Bryar, quotetype:PLAIN]
Start with the customer experience and work backwards to the technology.

